# 🎨 Crewera Reality — Frontend File Structure (Next.js + JSX)

> **Next.js 14 (App Router)** · JavaScript/JSX Only · No TypeScript

---

## 📁 Root Structure

```
D:\CREWERA\frontend\
├── 📄 package.json
├── 📄 jsconfig.json                      ← Path aliases (@/components, @/lib)
├── 📄 next.config.js
├── 📄 .env.local
├── 📄 .eslintrc.json
│
├── 📁 public/                            ← Static assets
├── 📁 app/                               ← Next.js App Router (pages)
├── 📁 components/                        ← Reusable components
├── 📁 lib/                               ← API calls, utilities, hooks
└── 📁 styles/                            ← Global CSS
```

---

## 📁 public/

```
public/
├── 📁 images/
│   ├── logo.svg
│   ├── logo-white.svg
│   ├── hero-bg.jpg
│   ├── placeholder-property.jpg
│   ├── placeholder-avatar.png
│   └── 📁 icons/                  # Amenity icons, feature icons
├── 📁 fonts/                      # Self-hosted fonts (DM Sans, Poppins)
├── favicon.ico
├── robots.txt
└── sitemap.xml
```

---

## 📁 styles/

```
styles/
├── 📄 globals.css                 # CSS reset, variables, typography, dark mode
├── 📄 animations.css              # Keyframes, transitions, micro-interactions
├── 📄 map.css                     # Google Map styles (from your existing style.css)
└── 📄 property-detail.css         # Property detail page styles (from your property.html)
```

---

## 📁 app/ — Pages & Layouts

### Root Layout & Global Pages

```
app/
├── 📄 layout.js                   # Root layout: <html>, fonts, Navbar, Footer, Toaster
├── 📄 globals.css                 # Imported in layout
├── 📄 page.js                     # ← HOME PAGE
├── 📄 not-found.js                # Custom 404
├── 📄 loading.js                  # Global loading spinner
├── 📄 error.js                    # Global error boundary
```

---

### 🏠 HOME PAGE — `app/page.js`

| Section | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| **Hero Banner** | Full-width video/image with search overlay (city, type, budget) |
| **Quick Search Bar** | City, Property Type, BHK, Budget → redirects to `/properties` |
| **Featured Properties** | Carousel of featured/premium properties |
| **Property Types** | Visual cards: Apartment, Villa, Commercial, etc. |
| **Why Choose Us** | Stats counters (properties, happy clients, cities) |
| **Trending Properties** | Properties sorted by analytics trending_score |
| **Testimonials Carousel** | Approved testimonials with ratings |
| **Latest Blog Posts** | 3 recent blog cards |
| **Newsletter CTA** | Email input for newsletter subscription |
| **FAQ Accordion** | Top 5 frequently asked questions |

---

### 🔍 PROPERTIES (Map + List) — `app/properties/`

> **This integrates your existing Google Maps Feature v6**

```
app/properties/
├── 📄 page.js                     # ← PROPERTIES LISTING PAGE (Map + Sidebar)
└── 📄 layout.js                   # Properties-specific layout (no footer, full height)
```

| Section | Functionality (from your v6) |
|---------|------------------------------|
| **Filter Bar** | Search, City, Type, Price (popover + slider), Status, Bedrooms (popover), Sort |
| **Map Tools** | Draw polygon, clear polygon, bounds filter |
| **Favorites Button** | Heart icon with count badge |
| **Active Filter Badges** | Removable pills showing applied filters |
| **Google Map (Left)** | Markers with price labels, marker clustering, info window |
| **Property Cards (Right Sidebar)** | Infinite scroll cards with image, price, BHK, area |
| **More Filters Panel** | Slide-in: area, builder, furnished, sample house, virtual tour, sq.ft range |
| **Compare Bar** | Bottom bar: selected properties for comparison |
| **Compare Modal** | Side-by-side property comparison table |
| **Favorites Panel** | Right slide-in panel with saved favorites |

---

### 🏢 PROPERTY DETAIL — `app/properties/[slug]/`

> **This integrates your existing property.html multi-tab design**

```
app/properties/[slug]/
└── 📄 page.js                     # ← SINGLE PROPERTY DETAIL PAGE
```

| Tab | Sections & Functionality |
|-----|--------------------------|
| **Overview** | Image gallery (5 photos + labels), video player, about text, key stats (BHK, area, price, status, RERA), seller card with rating |
| **Floor Plans** | BHK tabs → variant cards (carpet, SBA, price/sqft, units, lifts, parking, balconies) with floorplan images |
| **Amenities** | Grid of amenity icons grouped by category |
| **Location** | Google Map with marker, nearby places (hospital, school, metro, airport), street view |
| **Specifications** | Accordion: Electrification, Flooring, Toilets, Windows, Doors, Kitchen, Walls |
| **Price Trends** | Chart.js line chart of price history over time |
| **Reviews** | User reviews with multi-star ratings (overall, construction, location, amenities, value) |
| **Similar Projects** | Horizontal carousel of similar property cards |
| **Inquiry Sidebar** | Sticky form: name, email, phone, message → inquiry API |
| **Share/Favorite** | Share buttons (WhatsApp, copy link), favorite toggle |

---

### 📝 AUTH PAGES — `app/(auth)/`

```
app/(auth)/
├── 📄 layout.js                   # Auth layout (centered card, no navbar)
├── login/
│   └── 📄 page.js                 # Login form (email, password, remember me)
├── register/
│   └── 📄 page.js                 # Registration form (name, email, phone, password)
├── forgot-password/
│   └── 📄 page.js                 # Forgot password (email input)
├── reset-password/
│   └── 📄 page.js                 # Reset password (new password + confirm)
└── verify-email/
    └── 📄 page.js                 # Email verification status page
```

