### 📰 BLOG — `app/blog/`

```
app/blog/
├── 📄 page.js                     # Blog listing: featured post hero + grid + category filter
├── categories/
│   └── [slug]/
│       └── 📄 page.js             # Posts filtered by category
└── [slug]/
    └── 📄 page.js                 # Single blog post: content, author, comments, related posts
```

| Section | Functionality |
|---------|---------------|
| **Blog Listing** | Featured hero + paginated grid, sidebar categories |
| **Single Post** | Rich content, featured image, reading time, author card |
| **Comments** | Threaded comments with reply, name/email required |
| **Related Posts** | 3 related posts at bottom |

