## 📁 lib/

```
lib/
├── 📁 api/                        # API service functions (axios/fetch calls)
│   ├── 📄 client.js               # Axios instance with baseURL, interceptors, auth token
│   ├── 📄 auth.js                 # login, register, logout, resetPassword, verifyEmail
│   ├── 📄 users.js                # getProfile, updateProfile, getPreferences, updatePrefs
│   ├── 📄 properties.js           # list, getBySlug, search, featured, trending, nearby
│   ├── 📄 propertyAdmin.js        # create, update, delete, updateStatus, sub-table CRUD
│   ├── 📄 pricing.js              # getPricing, addPricing, updatePricing, deletePricing
│   ├── 📄 media.js                # uploadMedia, deleteMedia, setPrimary
│   ├── 📄 reviews.js              # getReviews, submitReview, markHelpful, report
│   ├── 📄 leads.js                # getLeads, updateStatus, assign, followUp
│   ├── 📄 inquiries.js            # submitInquiry, getInquiries, reply
│   ├── 📄 propertyRequests.js     # submit, getOwn, complete, adminReview
│   ├── 📄 favorites.js            # add, remove, check, list
│   ├── 📄 comparisons.js          # create, update, delete, list
│   ├── 📄 blog.js                 # getPosts, getBySlug, comments, categories
│   ├── 📄 content.js              # testimonials, faqs, contactMessages
│   ├── 📄 notifications.js        # get, markRead, delete, send, templates
│   ├── 📄 analytics.js            # dashboard, propertyAnalytics, marketTrends
│   ├── 📄 audit.js                # auditLogs, activity, loginHistory
│   ├── 📄 tags.js                 # getTags, create, update, delete
│   └── 📄 savedSearches.js        # create, list, update, delete, runSearch
│
├── 📁 hooks/                      # Custom React hooks
│   ├── 📄 useAuth.js              # Auth state, login, logout, isAdmin
│   ├── 📄 useApi.js               # Generic API fetch hook with loading/error
│   ├── 📄 useFavorites.js         # Favorites state management
│   ├── 📄 useCompare.js           # Compare list state management
│   ├── 📄 useFilters.js           # Property filters state + URL sync
│   ├── 📄 useMap.js               # Google Maps init, markers, polygon
│   ├── 📄 useInfiniteScroll.js    # Infinite scroll pagination
│   ├── 📄 useToast.js             # Toast notification state
│   ├── 📄 useDebounce.js          # Input debounce
│   ├── 📄 useMediaQuery.js        # Responsive breakpoint detection
│   └── 📄 useLocalStorage.js      # Persistent local storage state
│
├── 📁 context/                    # React Context providers
│   ├── 📄 AuthContext.js          # Auth provider: user, token, isLogged, isAdmin
│   ├── 📄 ThemeContext.js         # Dark mode toggle
│   ├── 📄 FavoritesContext.js     # Global favorites state
│   └── 📄 NotificationContext.js  # Unread notifications count
│
├── 📁 utils/
│   ├── 📄 formatters.js           # formatPrice(₹), formatDate, formatArea(sqft)
│   ├── 📄 validators.js           # Form validation helpers
│   ├── 📄 constants.js            # Enums, dropdown options, status colors
│   ├── 📄 mapUtils.js             # Map helpers (bounds, polygon, distance)
│   └── 📄 seo.js                  # Generate meta tags, structured data
│
└── 📄 middleware.js               # Next.js middleware: auth redirect, admin guard
```

---

## 📊 Page & Feature Summary

| Page | Route | Key Features |
|------|-------|-------------|
| Home | `/` | Hero, search bar, featured properties, testimonials, blog, FAQ |
| Properties | `/properties` | **Google Map + filters + sidebar + compare + favorites** |
| Property Detail | `/properties/[slug]` | **Multi-tab: gallery, floor plans, amenities, map, specs, price chart, reviews** |
| Login | `/login` | Email/password form |
| Register | `/register` | Registration form |
| User Dashboard | `/dashboard` | Activity overview |
| Profile | `/profile` | Edit profile (16 fields) |
| Preferences | `/preferences` | Notification/privacy/display toggles |
| Favorites | `/favorites` | Favorited properties grid |
| My Inquiries | `/inquiries` | Inquiry list + admin responses |
| Submit Request | `/property-requests/new` | **5-step wizard (ROI compulsory)** |
| Complete Request | `/property-requests/[id]/complete` | **8-section completion form (post-approval)** |
| Blog | `/blog` | Post listing + categories |
| Blog Post | `/blog/[slug]` | Full post + comments |
| Contact | `/contact` | Contact form + map |
| FAQs | `/faqs` | Accordion by category |
| **Admin Dashboard** | `/admin` | **KPI cards, charts, activity feed** |
| Admin Users | `/admin/users` | User management table |
| Admin Properties | `/admin/properties` | Properties table + quick actions |
| Admin Add Property | `/admin/properties/new` | **8-step wizard form** |
| Admin Requests | `/admin/property-requests` | **ROI review + approve/reject** |
| Admin Leads | `/admin/leads` | **Kanban board + pipeline** |
| Admin Blog | `/admin/blog` | Post editor + categories + comments |
| Admin Analytics | `/admin/analytics` | Deep analytics + city heatmap |
| Admin Audit | `/admin/audit-logs` | Audit trail table |

